\emph on
But can also be much more exotic.
\end_layout

\end_inset

Example:
\emph default
 exchange option on two thoroughbreds:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{Payoff}=\begin{cases}
\text{Horse }1 & \text{if Horse }1\text{ is better than Horse }2\\
\text{Horse }2 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
\]

